etc.aloe.data
Class SegmentSet

java.lang.Object
  etc.aloe.data.SegmentSet

public class SegmentSet
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a collection of segments. Knows how to transform itself into Weka Instances with basic feature information.

getBasicExamples

public ExampleSet getBasicExamples()
Convert the segment set into an ExampleSet (ready for feature extraction). The returned example set includes an id attribute, the message text, a label attribute, and several basic features extracted from the segment.
